title: Top 12 QB Countdown + Ultimate Draft Week, Dynasty Download - Fantasy Football Podcast for 4/26
description:
Ultimate Draft Week is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, exciting announcements up top before Andy, Mike, and Jason reveal their early QB rankings! Plus, a pre-NFL Draft edition of Dynasty Download! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for April 26th, 2022.

The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+

(01:20) - Ultimate Draft Week!
(05:20) - NFL News
(14:15) - Early QB Rankings
(15:20) - Matthew Stafford
(19:20) - Jalen Hurts
(23:20) - Aaron Rodgers
(27:00) - Joe Burrow
(31:40) - Dak Prescott
(34:25) - Tom Brady
(39:10) - Russell Wilson
(42:05) - Lamar Jackson
(44:50) - Kyler Murray
(48:15) - Patrick Mahomes
(49:55) - Justin Herbert
(52:40) - Josh Allen
(55:45) - Dynasty Download
